    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1941-11-24T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1941-11-24T00:00:00-05:00" n="472"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d472">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.94/2471</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to President
                            <persName type="to">Roosevelt</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-11-24">November 24,
                            1941</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>There is attached for your consideration a draft of a message to the British
                    Prime Minister<note n="78" xml:id="d472fn78">See telegram No. 5392, <hi
                            rend="italic">infra.</hi>
                    </note> containing a description of a proposal for a <hi rend="italic">modus
                        vivendi</hi> made by the Japanese Government to this Government and of a
                    suggested alternate <hi rend="italic">modus vivendi</hi> which this Government
                    proposes to offer to the Japanese Government.</p>
                <p>If you approve of the draft telegram, I shall arrange to have it forwarded.<note
                        n="79" xml:id="d472fn79">President Roosevelt’s notation: “OK. See addition.
                        FDR”. For addition, see close of telegram, <hi rend="italic"
                        >infra</hi>.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>C[<hi rend="smallcaps">ordell</hi>] H[<hi rend="smallcaps"
                        >ull</hi>]</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
